data.description: Here is a cute solid house just a short distance to Henderson Center that is move in ready. Starting with redwood framed construction and including oak floors under existing floors, plus newer appliances, new paint in and out, this home is ready for your enjoyment. Also there are new vinyl windows, a new sliding glass door, new front and rear doors, and a large rear yard. The garage was converted to a new room with a laundry room and space for either hobbies, an office or a are a third bedroom. Add to that the forced air heater installed in 2010, the tile countertops, and you have a house needing little maintenance in the near future.  Home is very energy efficient with blown in insulation in the walls along with the efficient heater. Yes, here is a fine home and a good investment.
